Summary: Orangle/Amber Lights Over the Skies again
divs: sighting detailswas out back talking on the phone when i saw a row of 3 orange lights come on in a slanted angle. they came back on again about 5 minutes later as a single light, then came on a 3rd time time in a different part of the sky but same general area but this time it was very bright. was south\se of abilene texas. same orange lights that have been coming on around here for 2 years now, i last saw these lights on october 8th 2010. keep your eyes out people, they don't stay on very long. they come on and fade right back out within' 1-2 seconds.
